---
import { ArrowRight } from "lucide-react";
---
<section class="py-20 bg-brand-navy text-center px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Planning an Enterprise Learning Initiative?</h2>
    <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 mb-10 leading-relaxed">
      Share your audiences, learning goals, existing content, preferred platform and project requirements. TheEduAssist will review the information and recommend a practical starting point.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4">
      <a href="/enterprise-solutions/project-brief/" class="inline-flex justify-center items-center px-8 py-4 border border-transparent text-lg font-bold rounded-md text-brand-navy bg-brand-green hover:bg-green-500 transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-brand-green focus:ring-offset-brand-navy max-w-full overflow-hidden">
        Submit an Enterprise Project Brief
        <ArrowRight className="ml-2 -mr-1 w-5 h-5 flex-shrink-0" />
      </a>
      <a href="/contact/" class="inline-flex justify-center items-center px-8 py-4 border border-slate-500 text-lg font-bold rounded-md text-white hover:bg-slate-800 transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-slate-500 focus:ring-offset-brand-navy max-w-full overflow-hidden">
        Contact Our Team
      </a>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-8 max-w-full overflow-hidden">
       <a href="/services/" class="text-slate-400 hover:text-white font-medium transition-colors underline underline-offset-4 decoration-slate-600">
         Explore All Services
       </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
